re. Yes, we only used to spend a few months in the autumn. Went there after the London season. And then we went abroad always - about - what, somewhere in October. So we - we were very little there. That's why I think - I say we weren't t}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15945211\charrsid12720898 y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 pical because - I
 mean, if - if we'd lived the normal - life of a peer on this - estate, I suppose one would have probably known - one would have known - farmer's children wouldn't one and - village children, people like that, you see, they - didn't come into our lives at
 all, because we weren't there enough.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Did you know of the children of other people, other aristocrats and that sort of thing?
