\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Yes. Well he wrote - he wrote a lot of children}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15945211\charrsid12720898 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 
