here's something - Curdie and the - Princess and Curdie, all this. Yes, I think so. Well - oh there were a great many of course we poured over them because - of him being the local celebrity. I think - he ended up with religious mania didn't he as far as 
I know. Probably that'd come in his bio - I think he did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Did he tell stories to you at all?
