No, I don't remember that. He was - really almost too grand and respected, you know, one was rather frightened of him, in my day, I suppose he was very old by then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 You said your mother was about thirty when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 How old was your father when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Same - he was the same age. Exact, I mean the same month even.
