canvassing in Brixton - for an election, but I suppose that would be in Debrett or something. Yes. What I can't remember was if he got in. And I think he may have been in for a very short time, just before - my grandfather died. But I know that - they wer
e a lot in - in England at one time when - we were in a house they'd - taken in - Ireland And that we were separated a lot because - of political campaigning.
