I adored it, yes. Oh that was my only reason for liking - living at Hornby because - only - place I ride, we couldn't ride at Bordighera, so - I did love that and longed to hunt. Didn't - wasn't able to - I was quite - oh about eighteen I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Was there a sort of age limit that prevented you from riding until eighteen?
