Oh no, it wasn't that, it just didn't - work out because - my father - we weren't enough at Hornby and it wasn't 'til I went and stayed with a - 
married sister, and then my father lent me - a couple of hunters to - hunt with her. No, it wasn't otherwise the age limit.
\par 
