\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 No. No, not study, a room - where you keep 
- papers and documents and - just - well it's gone from me for the moment, but - yes. Well then the back premises - I - you see, were vast I suppose. But - one didn't know a great many of them, one didn't go into them all you know. I can - the still room 
was somewhere on the estate and I can remember that. But for instance I don't remember the kitchen, 'cos I haven't seen the kitchen.
