\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 It must have been an extreme change for you, and a lot of other girls too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Well I mean I think my mother - just took it - quite in her stride, and my father was away on a ship, he was - in the RNVR
 and was on - at sea most of the - most of the war, and I don't think he was really conscious of it, because I can remember after years in the war him being back on leave, and us lunching together at - Clarages, and that I'd just got to get home to Grosve
nor Crescent or somewhere, it's not very far, and then - saying he'd got to go - somewhere else, now how are you going to get home? So I said, oh I'll just - walk home, but - not alone. This was the - he hadn't been at all conscious of it.
