- wasn't his affair, either politically or - really - intellectually. But my sister had made - a great friends with - somebody who married Raymond Asquith, Katherine Asquith, she's still alive I think. And - so we knew all the Asquith - brothers very well
 
and I came out to that. In fact I remember making very inappropriate suggestion with the same Aunt Maud - Lansdowne - read it lightly darling - one - who - we were going to stay with them at - Lansdowne abode, and she said, would we ask - ask two - would 
