les. Because - you always pretended you hadn't the band again, you know, 'cos you - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15945211\charrsid12720898 sitting}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 
 out - you sat out on the stairs, maybe the - you know sitting room might be full up, and so - stairs was sitting out place, well if you reached the top storey you -
 really - probably didn't hear the - music, because I did get left behind at my first dance for that reason. 'Cos I hadn't heard, because we - were - sitting out on the stairs.
