n with sixpence a week - I think when one was about six, and I rather think we only increased by a penny a year or something. But - I don't remember particularly - though I have a feeling we had some sort of charity parties - in Italy - for - some childre
n, poor children there. - I don't remember it very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 You don't ever remember anybody telling you that you ought to do some weeding or tidy up your room regularly or those sort of things?

