I - no, I can remember her doing much later with my brother, I don't remember it - myself. I feel she probably did, but I don't - it's not something I remember. Don't hav
e a very viv - vivid memory of - meal - meals and mealtime really. Mealtimes seem to have been some children very fraught with sort of lots of rules and also being made to eat food they didn't like and that sort of thing. Oh. Oh I think, yes, I can rememb
e
r that, I'm sure one was made to eat one's milky pudding - and things of that sort. And I - and also - perhaps a - really - and more milk than one wanted, I think I was rather - thin, I can remember - quite a lot of feeding doubts that I was - made to - h
a
ve, but I disliked, yes, and some moment when I had to have, - mutton chop one day and beef steak the next alternately - nothing else do you - I mean - and one got sick of that. And - then of course - wine was given I can remember - also - having - port a
t eleven. Quite small, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 To strengthen you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 
Yes. I mean really - quite small. And I - I - think red wine occasionally at meals but I - that I won't swear. Port is what I remember. Chiefly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Did you like it at that age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Yes, I think I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Because it's quite sweet I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 What about beer at meals, did you ever have beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 I don't ever remember that. Don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Were your meals fairly plain, you talked about having beef steak and things like that, were they - ?
\par 
