Yes, they were supposed to be but - Barty used to spoil me - and - let me come and have - when I'd had my - biscuits and milk before going to bed - I'd go and sit with her - while she had her dinner, which was rich and varied, and 
- because she spoilt me a lot she used to - feed me on hers too and there was - crisis - when - she had to be forbidden to do it because it was upsetting - and her feelings were very hurt. I remember that. That was when I saw about - seven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 When you were that age did you have a sort of hot meal at midday and then a kind of light tea?
