 the cake, all that. I have a sort of feeling - that one did have to eat plain - some plain bread and butter, but I may be - just thinking of books. And - luncheon and then I say - what was called supper - was I think probably - biscuits and - milk and th
ings of that sort.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Just before going to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Yes.
