n't think one ate - one didn't eat very many sweets, well we didn't I don't think you know, we had to - I think we did have to buy our - sweets weren't around, except - at Christmas or - something special bought. Otherwise I think one bought it - bought s
ome with one's sixpence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Do you remember if anything like bread or jam was made at Hornby in the house?
