\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Yes. Wasn't there supposed - it was something - yes. I think there was. You either had
 the beer or the allow - allowance for it, I think, as far as I remember. That I should - imagine was for the un}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1012224\charrsid12720898 der}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 
 - servants. The top ones I think probably had it anyhow I don't know. 'Cos - ste}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1012224\charrsid12720898 w}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 ards room I mean was very grand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Do you remember if there was a kitchen garden where the household vegetables were grown?
