Oh yes. The kitchen garden was a - long way from the house, they all - always seemed to be didn't they, those big houses, the same at Trafalgar. That - oh I remember the kitchen garden well. And I suppose we had vegetables and fruit - sent up from there.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Did you have peaches and grapes and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Yes. There were - I think quite a lot of - hot houses.
