 a child expected to be quite when grownups were talking, if you were in a room with your mother and her friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Well I think - we were rather shy - as children, so I think it - that we probably - were silent - anyway. I think we would have been tol
d not to - make a noise but - I don't remember it particularly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 You don't ever remember being sort of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1012224\charrsid12720898 sho}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 ed out of a room or anything like that?
