\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 No, I don't know - particularly remember that.
