\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 
Oh Dorothy and I - one period I think used to quarrel quite a lot. Oh yes, we did. I think when we were small - younger, before she rather moved herself - to the school of - with Olga. And - we gought. I've early nursery memories - of fighting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Actually fighting fisticuffs?
