 an hour's rest or half an hour's rest whatever it was, and I've still a memory of hearing - my sister Dorothy calling to Barty and saying - oh she's saying, what's going on, you're making a noise, I know you're moving about. And Dorothy saying - well, Mo
i
ra - will - spit in my face. And Barty'd say - well Darling, lovey-dovey, turn the other way. So then again - more - talk - what it - why - aren't you quite and resting? Because Moira will kick me in the back. So that I was evidently very naughty at that 
