 - I don't think I probably did go to a funeral before the - that first war. I can't - were much - lot of old relations must have died but I - don't particularly remember going to their funeral.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 Do you remember wearing mourning at a later date than that, when Edward the VII for example?
