at we liked very much, somebody called Granny Abercorn who lived 'til - well over ninety - and we were very fond of. But I can't remember wearing - mourning for her, 'cos I - can remember - when she died. I don't remember whether we wore mourning. I think
 probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1054659 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 But you don't actually remember it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5195713 ML  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2701124\charrsid12720898 No.
